The line of thought is that `map_id Y` requires proving `(fun g => comp g (id Y)) = id (Hom c Y)`.
The `funext` tactic is used to introduce an arbitrary `g : Hom c Y`. The goal becomes `comp g (id Y) = id (Hom c Y) g`.
